dwm rule 配置 方法
用于配置某个app在固定的tag打开
比如：无论在哪里打开firefox，firerfox都会显示在tag2

dwm rule 描述
暂时只用到 WM_CLASS 的第二个值：class
WM_CLASS(STRING) = instance, class
WM_NAME(STRING) = title

获取 WM_CLASS WM_NAME 的方法
执行命令：xprop
鼠标变成十字形
点击app窗口
终端打印app窗口信息

firefox
WM_CLASS(STRING) = "Navigator", "firefox-esr"
WM_NAME(COMPOUND_TEXT) = "Dwm rules array explanation · GitHub Copilot — Mozilla Firefox"

thunar
WM_CLASS(STRING) = "thunar", "Thunar"
WM_NAME(STRING) = "cofon - Thunar"

mousepad
WM_CLASS(STRING) = "mousepad", "Mousepad"
WM_NAME(COMPOUND_TEXT) = "未命名 1 - Mousepad"
